data.description: Snowbirds & Investors Alert... This beautiful completely renovated 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom condo with 1,050sqft and a large community in-ground swimming pool is in El'Conquistador Condominiums. Located perfectly between ' The Worlds Most Famous Beach' Daytona Beach and the Halifax River allowing for a short walk/bike ride to watch the sunrise in the ocean and sunset in the river. This unit has new vinyl plank flooring throughout, new light fixtures and new paint through entire interior. Both bathrooms have been completely remodeled. The kitchen has been updated with new cabinetry, granite counter tops and a complete new stainless steel appliance package.
